YUI Tutorial written using ReST/Sphinx.

Instructions for setting up Sphinx in a virtualenv. Skip steps 1-3 if you are not using MacPorts.

1. Install MacPorts
2. sudo port install python26 py26-setuptools
3. Edit your $PATH to include /opt/local/bin followed by /opt/local/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/2.6/bin
4. sudo easy_install -UZ pip
5. sudo pip install virtualenv virtualenvwrapper
6. virtualenv ~/docs
7. cd docs
8. source bin/activate
9. pip install sphinx (note: no more sudo!
10. mkdir yui_tutoral, cd, git init, pull yui_tutorial
11. make html
